  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was a-- so it was a very-- it was a very-- so full of tragedies.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You-- every day you would hear another story.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "People were talking about concentration.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We became aware that 1945, when we came back to Poland, we were aware what was happening.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I mean and the Poles sort of tried.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The situation was that the Poles were very-- in Katowice I've seen things like with the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That the Poles would put them in camps and prisons, which we felt was very justified.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But still for us, it was many Jews tried to get out of Poland, as I said before.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I wanted to study-- you know my dream was to study.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And now I could feel that for the first time in my life I had all the opportunities, because I got a scholarship.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
